==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Rotund
<hw>Ro*tund"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>rotundus</ets>. See <er>Round</er>, and cf.
<er>Rotunda</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Round; circular;
spherical.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Hence, complete; entire.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>orbicular, or nearly so.</def>
<rj><au>Gray.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Rotund</ent>⟦br⟧

